<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10438000>
    dc:description "FIGURE 56. Collected specimens (A, B), and distribution in southeastern Brazil and adjacent areas (C, D). Nepomorpha, Gelastocoridae from Campos dos Goytacazes, Rio de Janeiro (−21.7469, −41.4994), males. A, C. Gelastocoris flavus flavus. B, D. Nerthra nepaeformis. Stars indicate new records; circles indicate previous records; question marks indicate unspecified locality. Scale bars: 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10438000/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

